List all bank accounts for the Plaid Item.

```python
result = await connector.get_accounts()
for account in result["accounts"]:
    print(account["name"], account["mask"])
```

**Plaid endpoint:** `POST /accounts/get`

**Returns:**
```json
{
  "accounts": [
    {
      "account_id": "acct_abc123",
      "name": "Plaid Checking",
      "mask": "0000",
      "type": "depository",
      "subtype": "checking",
      "balances": { "current": 110.01, "available": 100.00, "iso_currency_code": "USD" }
    }
  ]
}
```
